  "text": "Current clinical evidence also points to CIK cells as a potentially useful immunotherapy approach for cancer patients. Similar to other forms of immunotherapy, the infusion of CIK cells may be more efficacious at disease stages where the tumor burden is relatively low or in an adjuvant setting, rather than for advanced disease [CITATION_1] .",
